Hey :) here are some extra tips 

1. Use 2 or more slurppers/bangers at time so 1 can soak while you dab with the other and change after every dab. 
2. Don’t dunk while the slurpper is too hot cause it can catch fire again if that happens smoother the fire with the lid
3. When drying the slurpper before use heat the stem so all the alcohol while evaporate and not drain into your rig!! 
4. Buy a decent banger I am a fan of @banger.supply been using them for months and they stay clean if you keep em clean!! 

If you want and example if these tips I can make a Pt. 2!!!
